Package: ggnetwork
Type: Package
Title: Geometries to plot networks with ggplot2
Version: 0.2.1
Date: 2015-10-26
Author: Francois Briatte
Maintainer: Francois Briatte <f.briatte@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides four geoms to plot network objects with ggplot2. The vignette bundled with the package provides a complete guide to how these geoms work.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
VignetteBuilder: knitr
NeedsCompilation: no
Depends:
  ggplot2 (>= 1.0.1.9003),
  R (>= 2.14),
Imports:
  network,
  sna
Suggests:
  intergraph,
  knitr,
  testthat
